{BLOCKER} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature to this creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, draw a card. Then you may put a non-evolution light creature that costs 7 or less from your hand into the battle zone.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, choose one of your opponent's shields and put it into their graveyard.
■ Revolution 2—If you have 2 shields or less, each of your darkness creatures gets "blocker" and "slayer".

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ You may summon this creature from your mana zone.
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, for each of your creatures in the battle zone, you may put a nature Invader evolution creature from your mana zone on top of that creature tapped.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
{SHIELD SAVER} (When one of your shields would be broken, you may destroy this creature instead.)
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, put one of your shields into your graveyard.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, return all of your shields to your hand. You can't use the "Shield Trigger" abilities of those shields. Then add the top 2 cards from your deck to your shields face down.
■ Revolution 2—If you have 2 shields or less, each of your light cards put into your hand from your shields gets "shield trigger".

{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ During your opponent's turn, whenever your opponent puts a card in their mana zone or whenever they use a card, skip the rest of their turn.
■ Whenever an opponent's creature attacks, after the attack, skip the rest of their turn.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, each player discards a card from their hand.
■ Revolution 2—Whenever a darkness creature is discarded from your hand, if you have 2 shields or less, put it into the battle zone.

{SPEED ATTACKER} (This creature doesn't get summoning sickness.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, choose 2 of your opponent's shields and this creature breaks the rest.
